## Locksmith Integration

This environment uses [Locksmith](https://github.com/lorem-dev/locksmith) for secure MCP secret management.

- Retrieve secrets: `locksmith get --key <alias>` (auto-starts a session if none is active)
- To reuse a session: export the session ID printed to stderr as `LOCKSMITH_SESSION`
- Sessions expire automatically by TTL - no need to end them manually
- Pass `LOCKSMITH_SESSION` to sub-agents so they share the parent session
